Import Dataset¶

In [23]:
import cv2
import numpy as np
import os
# read images in folder
def read_image(path, is_gray_scale=False, is_region_growing=False):
    x = []
    y = []
    # iterate through the names of contents of the folder
    for image_label in os.listdir(path):
        if is_region_growing:
          path_label = path+image_label+'/none/'
        else:
          path_label = path+image_label + '/'

        for image_path in os.listdir(path_label):
          # create the full input path and read the file
          # 0 is grayscale
          if(is_gray_scale):
            image = cv2.imread(path_label + image_path, 0)
          else:
            image = cv2.imread(path_label + image_path)

          try:
              # resize image => all images are the same size
              image = cv2.resize(image, (50,50))
              if is_gray_scale:
                image = image.flatten()
              x.append(image)
              y.append(image_label)
          except:
              continue

    return np.array(x), np.array(y)

Kesimpulan Hasil Analisis Dataset¶

  • Dateset tidak memiliki permasalahan keseimbangan label (imbalance)
  • data dengan label covid memiliki sebaran yang unik jika dibandingkan dengan label lainnya
  • diantara PCA dengan dimensi 30, 50, 100, dimensi dengan jumlah 50 memiliki generalisasi terbaik.

Praproses Data¶

Generate Data (Seeded Region Growing)¶

In [3]:
import random
import subprocess as sp
random.seed(1)

#fungsi merandom nama untuk menandai region
def random_color():
    r = random.randint(0,255)
    g = random.randint(0,255)
    b = random.randint(0,255)
    return r,g,b

#fungsi 
def get8neighbors(x,y,shape):
    #output variabel
    coor = [] 
    
    #borderline
    maxx = shape[1]-1
    maxy = shape[0]-1
    minx = 0
    miny = 0

    #kiri atas ↖
    coorx = x - 1
    coory = y - 1
    if coorx <= maxx and coorx >= minx and coory <= maxy and coory >= miny:
        coor.append((coorx,coory))

    #atas tengah ↑
    coorx = x
    coory = y - 1
    if coorx <= maxx and coorx >= minx and coory <= maxy and coory >= miny:
        coor.append((coorx,coory))

    #atas kanan ↗
    coorx = x + 1
    coory = y - 1
    if coorx <= maxx and coorx >= minx and coory <= maxy and coory >= miny:
        coor.append((coorx,coory))

    #kiri ←
    coorx = x - 1
    coory = y
    if coorx <= maxx and coorx >= minx and coory <= maxy and coory >= miny:
        coor.append((coorx,coory))

    #kanan →
    coorx = x + 1
    coory = y
    if coorx <= maxx and coorx >= minx and coory <= maxy and coory >= miny:
        coor.append((coorx,coory))

    #bawah kiri ↙
    coorx = x - 1
    coory = y + 1
    if coorx <= maxx and coorx >= minx and coory <= maxy and coory >= miny:
        coor.append((coorx,coory))

    #bawah tengah ↓
    coorx = x
    coory = y + 1
    if coorx <= maxx and coorx >= minx and coory <= maxy and coory >= miny:
        coor.append((coorx,coory))

    #bawah kiri ↘
    coorx = x + 1
    coory = y + 1
    if coorx <= maxx and coorx >= minx and coory <= maxy and coory >= miny:
        coor.append((coorx,coory))

    return coor

#mencari nilai pixel maksimal pada cirta
def seed_point_search(pic):
    seed = -1 #inisiasi nilai seed
    for y, c in enumerate(pic):
        for x, d in enumerate(c):
            if pic[y][x] > seed:
                seed = pic[y][x]
    return seed 

#mencari koordinat seed
def seed_point_coor(seed,pic):
    list_coor = []
    for y, c in enumerate(pic):
        for x, _ in enumerate(c):
            if pic[y][x]  == seed:
                list_coor.append([y,x])
    return list_coor 

def region_growing(oripic,pic,seed,T,seedn):
    tmp = []
    resultimg = np.zeros_like(oripic) #penampung luaran segmentasi
    tmp.append((seed[0], seed[1]))
    processed = [] #penampung pixel yang sedang diproses
    r,g,b = random_color() #nilai untuk pewarnaan region
    pixel_counts = 0
    while(len(tmp) > 0):
        i = 0
        pix = tmp[0]
        #melakukan pengecekan kepada 8 tetangga pixel
        for coord in get8neighbors(pix[0], pix[1], pic.shape):
            if seedn - pic[coord[0], coord[1]] < T:
                resultimg[coord[0], coord[1],0] = b
                resultimg[coord[0], coord[1],1] = g
                resultimg[coord[0], coord[1],2] = r
                i += 1
                pixel_counts += 1
                #jika pixel yang akan diproses belum diproses sebelumnya
                if not coord in processed:
                    tmp.append(coord)
                #menambahkan daftar pixel yang sudah diproses dengan 8 tetangga
                processed.append(coord)
        tmp.pop(0)
        if i != 0:
            resultimg[pix[0], pix[1],0] = b
            resultimg[pix[0], pix[1],1] = g
            resultimg[pix[0], pix[1],2] = r
            pixel_counts += 1
    
    #minimal region yang diizinkan adalah 250 pixel
    # if pixel_counts < 50:
    #     resultimg = np.zeros_like(oripic)
        
    return resultimg

def segmentation_process(it,label,oripic,threshold):
    pic = cv2.cvtColor(oripic, cv2.COLOR_BGR2GRAY)
    # seedn = seed_point_search(pic)
    seedn = 255
    coor_seed = seed_point_coor(seedn,pic) 
    T = threshold
    result = np.zeros_like(oripic)
    #melakukan loop untuk semua koordinat seed
    for _, c in enumerate(coor_seed):
        if result[c[0]][c[1],].all() == 0:
            tmp = region_growing(oripic,pic,c,T,seedn)
            result = result + tmp

    #Menyimpan luaran segmentasi
    # dir_path = 'D:/kuliah/S2/"Semester 1"/"Pengenalan Pola"/Tugas/"Tugas 7 Tubes Final"/'
    path = 'dataset/T'+ str(threshold) + '/' + label + '/'
    
    #hanya hasil segmentasi
    gray_scale_result = cv2.cvtColor(result, cv2.COLOR_BGR2GRAY)
    cv2.imwrite(path+'none/'+str(it)+'.jpg',gray_scale_result)
    
    #hasil segmentasi berdampingan dengan citra asli
    result = np.hstack((oripic,result))
    cv2.imwrite(path+'join/'+str(it)+'.jpg',result)
In [29]:
import time
threshold_list = [60, 120, 180, 210, 240]
print('execution_time')
for threshold in threshold_list:
    start_time = time.time()
    for i in range(0, len(x_deep_learning)):
        segmentation_process(i,  y_deep_learning[i], x_deep_learning[i], threshold)
    exec_time = time.time() - start_time
    print('T' + str(threshold) + ' : ' + str(exec_time))

  • T210 dan T240 cenderung membuat sebaran label menjadi kurang variatif untuk kelas covid
  • T120 dan T180 memberikan jarak atau sebaran yang baik untuk setiap label
  • T60 membuat label selain covid menumpuk pada suatu sumbu x tertentu

Fungsi Plot Epoch¶

In [160]:
#visualisasi proses training
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from keras import backend as K

dir_grafik_cnn = ""
class TrainingPlot(keras.callbacks.Callback):
    # this function will be executed since the start
    def on_train_begin(self, logs={}):
        # do initialization
        self.losses = []
        self.accuracy = []
        self.val_losses = []
        self.val_accuracy = []
        self.logs = []

    # this function will be executed when epoch finished 
    def on_epoch_end(self, epoch, logs={}):
        # get the params of data
        self.logs.append(logs)
        self.losses.append(logs.get('loss'))
        self.accuracy.append(logs.get('accuracy'))
        self.val_losses.append(logs.get('val_loss'))
        self.val_accuracy.append(logs.get('val_accuracy'))
        
        if len(self.losses) > 1:
            N = np.arange(0, len(self.losses))
            # Ploting
            plt.plot(N, self.val_accuracy, 'y-', label="validation_accuracy")
            plt.plot(N, self.accuracy, 'b-', label="train_accuracy")
            plt.plot(N, self.losses, 'r-', label="train_loss")
            plt.plot(N, self.val_losses, 'g-', label="validation_loss")
                
            # show legend at first plot
            if(len(self.losses) == 2):
                plt.xlabel("Epoch #")
                plt.ylabel("Loss/Accuracy")
                plt.legend()
            # Save result to google drive
            plt.title("Loss & Accuracy [Epoch {}]".format(epoch+1))
            if((epoch + 1) % 50 == 0):
                plt.savefig(dir_grafik_cnn+'Epoch-{}.png'.format(epoch+1))
        
# Create object from TrainingPlot
plot_losses = TrainingPlot()
# Enter the matplotlib interactif mode  
plt.ion()

def recall_m(y_true, y_pred):
    true_positives = K.sum(K.round(K.clip(y_true * y_pred, 0, 1)))
    possible_positives = K.sum(K.round(K.clip(y_true, 0, 1)))
    recall = true_positives / (possible_positives + K.epsilon())
    return recall

def precision_m(y_true, y_pred):
    true_positives = K.sum(K.round(K.clip(y_true * y_pred, 0, 1)))
    predicted_positives = K.sum(K.round(K.clip(y_pred, 0, 1)))
    precision = true_positives / (predicted_positives + K.epsilon())
    return precision

def f1_m(y_true, y_pred):
    precision = precision_m(y_true, y_pred)
    recall = recall_m(y_true, y_pred)
    return 2*((precision*recall)/(precision+recall+K.epsilon()))

Arsitektur¶

menggunakan pre-trained model Xception

In [142]:
from tensorflow.keras.applications import MobileNetV2
from tensorflow.python.keras import layers
from tensorflow.python.keras import models

conv_base = MobileNetV2(weights='imagenet',
                  include_top=False,
                  input_shape=(50, 50, 3))

conv_base.trainable = True
model = models.Sequential()
model.add(conv_base)
model.add(layers.Flatten())
model.add(layers.Dropout(0.5))
model.add(layers.Dense(256, activation='relu'))
model.add(layers.Dense(4, activation='softmax'))

model.compile(loss='categorical_crossentropy', 
              optimizer='adam',
              metrics=['accuracy', f1_m, precision_m, recall_m])

WARNING:tensorflow:`input_shape` is undefined or non-square, or `rows` is not in [96, 128, 160, 192, 224]. Weights for input shape (224, 224) will be loaded as the default.
In [140]:
def log_cnn(teks):
    file1 = open('learning/cnn/hasil.txt','a')
    file1.write(teks + '\n')
    file1.close()

Training¶

In [161]:
from keras.callbacks import ModelCheckpoint
from sklearn.preprocessing import LabelBinarizer, LabelEncoder
from sklearn.metrics import confusion_matrix
labelEncoder = LabelEncoder()
labelBinarizer = LabelBinarizer()

for data in range(0, 1):
    ## data = 0 => original
    ## data = 1 => seeded region growing T120
    ## data = 2 => seeded region growing T180
    x_deep_cnn = []
    y_deep_cnn = []
    jenis_data = ""

    if(data == 0):
        x_deep_cnn = x_deep_learning
        y_deep_cnn = y_deep_learning
        jenis_data = 'original'

    if(data == 1):
        x_deep_cnn = x_srg_t120.reshape(50, 50, 1)
        y_deep_cnn = y_srg_t120
        jenis_data = 'T120'
    
    if(data == 2):
        x_deep_cnn = x_srg_t180
        y_deep_cnn = y_srg_t180
        jenis_data = 'T180'

    #encoding label
    y_deep_cnn = labelEncoder.fit_transform(y_deep_cnn)

    #Label Binerizing
    y_deep_cnn = labelBinarizer.fit_transform(y_deep_cnn)

    if(data != 0):
        log_cnn('\n')
    log_cnn(jenis_data)
    
    for fold in range(0, len(train_index_list)):
        checkpoint_path =  'learning/cnn/' + jenis_data + '/model/' + str(fold+1)
        dir_grafik_cnn = 'learning/cnn/' + jenis_data + '/grafik/' + str(fold+1) + '.png' 

        #create checkpoint object 
        # checkpoint = ModelCheckpoint(checkpoint_path, monitor='val_f1_m', verbose=1,
        #     save_best_only=True, mode='max')
        
        X_train, X_val = x_deep_cnn[train_index_list[fold],:],x_deep_cnn[val_index_list[fold],:]
        Y_train, Y_val = y_deep_cnn[train_index_list[fold]] , y_deep_cnn[val_index_list[fold]]

        hasil = model.fit(X_train, Y_train, validation_data=(X_val, Y_val),
            epochs=300, batch_size=302, callbacks=[plot_losses])
        
        loss, accuracy, f1_score, precision, recall = model.evaluate(X_val, Y_val, verbose=0)

        log_teks = 'Fold-' + str(fold+1) + ' : loss = ' + str(round(loss,4)) + ' acc = ' + \
            str(round(accuracy,4)) + ' f1_score = ' + str(round(f1_score,4)) + ' precision = ' + \
            str(round(precision,4)) + ' recall ' + str(round(recall,4))

        log_cnn(log_teks)
        plt.clf()

        # plot convusion matrix
        cf_matrix_path = 'learning/cnn/' + jenis_data + '/grafik/' + 'cf_' + str(fold+1) + '.png'
        Y_val_pred = model.predict(X_val)
        Y_val_pred = labelBinarizer.inverse_transform(Y_val_pred)
        Y_val = labelBinarizer.inverse_transform(Y_val)
        
        cf_matrix = confusion_matrix(Y_val_pred, Y_val, labels=[0, 1, 2, 3])
        cf_matrix = pd.DataFrame(cf_matrix, columns = ['covid', 'normal', 'pneumonia_bac', 'pneumonia_vir'], index= ['covid', 'normal', 'pneumonia_bac', 'pneumonia_vir'])
        cf_matrix = sns.heatmap(cf_matrix, annot=True)
        
        figure = cf_matrix.get_figure()    
        figure.savefig(cf_matrix_path, dpi=400)
        plt.clf()

In [198]:
def define_model():
    model = models.Sequential()
    model.add(layers.Conv2D(50, (3, 3), activation='relu', input_shape=(50, 50, 3)))
    model.add(layers.MaxPooling2D((2, 2)))
    model.add(layers.Conv2D(64, (3, 3), activation='relu'))
    model.add(layers.MaxPooling2D((2, 2)))
    model.add(layers.Conv2D(64, (3, 3), activation='relu'))
    model.add(layers.Flatten())
    model.add(layers.Dropout(0.5))
    model.add(layers.Dense(64, activation='relu'))
    model.add(layers.Dense(10))
    model.add(layers.Dense(4, activation='softmax'))
    model.compile(loss='categorical_crossentropy', 
        optimizer='adam', metrics=['accuracy', f1_m, precision_m, recall_m])

    return model

In [205]:
 #encoding label
y_deep_cnn = labelEncoder.fit_transform(y_deep_learning)

#Label Binerizing
y_deep_cnn = labelBinarizer.fit_transform(y_deep_cnn)

x_deep_cnn = x_deep_learning

for fold in range(0, len(train_index_list)):
    model = define_model()
    checkpoint_path =  'learning/cnn/model/' + str(fold+1)
    dir_grafik_cnn = 'learning/cnn/grafik/' + str(fold+1) + '.png' 

    #create checkpoint object 
    checkpoint = ModelCheckpoint(checkpoint_path, monitor='val_f1_m', verbose=1,
        save_best_only=True, mode='max')
    
    X_train, X_val = x_deep_cnn[train_index_list[fold],:],x_deep_cnn[val_index_list[fold],:]
    Y_train, Y_val = y_deep_cnn[train_index_list[fold]] , y_deep_cnn[val_index_list[fold]]

    hasil = model.fit(X_train, Y_train, validation_data=(X_val, Y_val),
        epochs=250, batch_size=300, callbacks=[plot_losses, checkpoint])
    
    loss, accuracy, f1_score, precision, recall = model.evaluate(X_val, Y_val, verbose=0)

    log_teks = 'Fold-' + str(fold+1) + ' : loss = ' + str(round(loss,4)) + ' acc = ' + \
        str(round(accuracy,4)) + ' f1_score = ' + str(round(f1_score,4)) + ' precision = ' + \
        str(round(precision,4)) + ' recall ' + str(round(recall,4))

    log_cnn(log_teks)
    plt.clf()

    # plot convusion matrix
    cf_matrix_path = 'learning/cnn/grafik/' + 'cf_' + str(fold+1) + '.png'
    Y_val_pred = model.predict(X_val)
    Y_val_pred = labelBinarizer.inverse_transform(Y_val_pred)
    Y_val = labelBinarizer.inverse_transform(Y_val)
    
    cf_matrix = confusion_matrix(Y_val_pred, Y_val, labels=[0, 1, 2, 3])
    cf_matrix = pd.DataFrame(cf_matrix, columns = ['covid', 'normal', 'pneumonia_bac', 'pneumonia_vir'], index= ['covid', 'normal', 'pneumonia_bac', 'pneumonia_vir'])
    plt.figure(figsize = (14,13))
    cf_matrix = sns.heatmap(cf_matrix, annot=True)
    figure = cf_matrix.get_figure()    
    
    figure.savefig(cf_matrix_path, dpi=400)
    plt.clf()

Kesimpulan CNN¶

  • Model pretrain MobileNetV2 tidak dapat memberikan hasil yang baik pada kasus ini
  • Luaran terbaik pada Fold ke 3 dengan akurasi dan F1 score = 0.876 dan 0.866
  • Terjadi overfit pada Fold ke 4

Decision Tree¶

In [39]:
def log_tree(teks):
    file1 = open('learning/decision_tree/hasil.txt','a')
    file1.write(teks + '\n')
    file1.close()
In [48]:
from sklearn import tree
from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score, f1_score

for jenis_data in range(0, 4):

    x_tree = []
    y_tree = []
    jenis_data_teks = ''
    if(jenis_data == 0):
        # normal
        x_tree = x
        y_tree = y
        jenis_data_teks = 'normal'

    elif(jenis_data == 1):
        # pc50
        x_tree = x_pca_50
        y_tree = y_pca_50
        jenis_data_teks = 'pc50'

    elif(jenis_data == 2):
        # T120
        x_tree = x_srg_t120
        y_tree = y_srg_t120
        jenis_data_teks = 't120'
    
    elif(jenis_data == 3):
        # T180
        x_tree = x_srg_t180
        y_tree = y_srg_t180
        jenis_data_teks = 't180'
    
    log_tree(jenis_data_teks)
    for fold in range(0, len(train_index_list)):
        cf_matrix_path = 'learning/decision_tree/' + jenis_data_teks + '_' + str(fold+1) + '.png'

        X_train, X_val = x_tree[train_index_list[fold],:], x_tree[val_index_list[fold],:]
        Y_train, Y_val = y_tree[train_index_list[fold]], y_tree[val_index_list[fold]]

        clf = tree.DecisionTreeClassifier()
        clf = clf.fit(X_train, Y_train)

        Y_pred = clf.predict(X_val)
        
        cf_matrix = confusion_matrix(Y_pred, Y_val, labels=['covid', 'normal', 'pneumonia_bacterial', 'pneumonia_viral'])
        cf_matrix = pd.DataFrame(cf_matrix, columns=['covid', 'normal', 'pneumonia_bacterial', 'pneumonia_viral'], index=['covid', 'normal', 'pneumonia_bacterial', 'pneumonia_viral'])
        plt.figure(figsize = (14,13))
        cf_matrix = sns.heatmap(cf_matrix, annot=True)
        figure = cf_matrix.get_figure()    
        
        figure.savefig(cf_matrix_path, dpi=400)

        akurasi = round(accuracy_score(Y_val, Y_pred), 4)
        f1 = round(f1_score(Y_val, Y_pred, zero_division=1, average='weighted'), 4)
        teks_log = 'Fold-' + str(fold+1) + ' : accuracy = ' + str(akurasi) + ' f1_score = ' + str(f1)
        log_tree(teks_log)

    log_tree('\n')

from sklearn import svm 

for jenis_data in range(0, 4):

    x_svm = []
    y_svm = []
    jenis_data_teks = ''

    if(jenis_data == 0):
        # normal
        x_svm = x
        y_svm = y
        jenis_data_teks = 'normal'

    elif(jenis_data == 1):
        # pc50
        x_svm = x_pca_50
        y_svm = y_pca_50
        jenis_data_teks = 'pc50'

    elif(jenis_data == 2):
        # T120
        x_svm = x_srg_t120
        y_svm = y_srg_t120
        jenis_data_teks = 't120'
    
    elif(jenis_data == 3):
        # T180
        x_svm = x_srg_t180
        y_svm = y_srg_t180
        jenis_data_teks = 't180'
    
    log_svm(jenis_data_teks)
    for fold in range(0, len(train_index_list)):
        cf_matrix_path = 'learning/svm/' + jenis_data_teks + '_' + str(fold+1) + '.png'

        X_train, X_val = x_svm[train_index_list[fold],:], x_svm[val_index_list[fold],:]
        Y_train, Y_val = y_svm[train_index_list[fold]], y_svm[val_index_list[fold]]

        clf = svm.SVC()
        clf = clf.fit(X_train, Y_train)

        Y_pred = clf.predict(X_val)
        
        cf_matrix = confusion_matrix(Y_pred, Y_val, labels=['covid', 'normal', 'pneumonia_bacterial', 'pneumonia_viral'])
        cf_matrix = pd.DataFrame(cf_matrix, columns=['covid', 'normal', 'pneumonia_bacterial', 'pneumonia_viral'], index=['covid', 'normal', 'pneumonia_bacterial', 'pneumonia_viral'])
        plt.figure(figsize = (14,13))
        cf_matrix = sns.heatmap(cf_matrix, annot=True)
        figure = cf_matrix.get_figure()    
        
        figure.savefig(cf_matrix_path, dpi=400)

        akurasi = round(accuracy_score(Y_val, Y_pred), 4)
        f1 = round(f1_score(Y_val, Y_pred, zero_division=1, average='weighted'), 4)
        teks_log = 'Fold-' + str(fold+1) + ' : accuracy = ' + str(akurasi) + ' f1_score = ' + str(f1)
        log_svm(teks_log)

    log_svm('\n')

Hasil dan Evaluasi¶

Internal¶

  • Luaran terbaik => CNN Fold 3
  • Luaran terburuk => SVM Fold 4 dengan data T120 (mengabaikan anomali pada CNN)
  • Seeded region growing memberikan performa yang buruk. Hal ini dikarenakan cirta X-ray yang diperoleh didapatkan dari banyak rumah sakit, jenis alat, dan kondisi yang berbeda. Hal ini menyebabkan pencayaan dan kualitas dari citra tidak seimbang dan memerlukan proses normalisasi tambahan
  • Data normal masih lebih baik dibandingkan dengan PCA 50 dimensi

Penelitian Terdahulu¶

Saran¶

  • Menggunakan dataset yang lebih besar. Saat ini sudah tersedia dataset x-ray pneumonia dan normal (tidak ada covid) dengan jumlah lebih dari 5000 instances. (https://www.kaggle.com/c/rsna-pneumonia-detection-challenge/overview)
  • Praproses citra dilakukan dengan algoritma yang tidak berhubungan dengan threshold skala keabuan. Atau bisa juga menggunakan algoritma untuk membuat normalisasi pencahayaan terlebih dahulu
